Copy one template from a source config item to a target config item. 
This tool will also ensure referenced global params and dependent single-select custom tables are copied to the target project/config when needed. 
Parameters: 
- sourceProjectId: Source project ID; 
- sourceConfigId: Source config item ID; 
- sourceTemplateId: Source template ID to copy; 
- projectId: Target project ID; 
- configId: Target config item ID. 
Returns true if the copy succeeds, false if the source template does not exist or the copy operation fails.

