Batch manage Hermes config strategies with one unified tool. 
Supported actions: online, offline, suspend, delete, approve, deny, cancel. 
Parameter rules: 
- strategyUuidList is used for online/offline/suspend/delete; 
- strategyList and optional reason are used for approve/deny/cancel; 
- online: strategies mapping status must be pending approval or draft; 
- offline: strategies mapping status must be online or suspend; 
- suspend: strategies mapping status must be online; 
- delete: strategies mapping status must not be running; 
- approve/deny/cancel: strategies mapping status must be pending approval. 
Returns a ConfigStrategyBatchOpResultDTO object containing successCount, failCount, errorMsg, and strategyUuidList.

