Batch manage Hermes flows with one unified tool. 
Supported actions: approve, deny, cancel, pause, recover, end. 
Parameter rules: 
- flowList and optional reason are used for approve/deny/cancel; 
- pauseFlowList is used for pause; 
- flowIdList is used for recover/end; 
- approve/deny/cancel: flows mapping status must be pending approval; 
- pause: flows mapping status must be waiting or running; 
- recover: flows mapping status must be pending; 
- end: flows mapping status must not be draft. 
Returns a FlowBatchOpResultDTO object containing successCount, failCount, errorMsg, and flowUuidList.

