description:
Manage Hermes operation tasks with one unified tool. 
Supported actions: send, pause, end, approve, deny, cancel. 
Common required parameters: projectId, taskId, action. 
Parameter rules: 
- reason is used only for review actions approve/deny/cancel, and ignored for send/pause/end; 
- send: task trigger type must be manual and mapping status must be waiting; 
- pause: task mapping status must be working; 
- end: task mapping status must be working or pending; 
- approve/deny/cancel: task mapping status must be pending approve. 
Returns true if the action succeeds, false if the operation fails or the task state is invalid.
